snippet.title: Match Three Pirates! Heir to Davy Jones coming to Steam next week
snippet.description:
Davy Jones was a pirate, who didn’t want to die. He wished to plow the sea forever. And he raised the dark forces and create own magic world - a Davy Jones’ Locker where there was no time and no one was getting old, and Davy was opening portals to our world to lure people into Davy Jones’ Locker to be a pirates and play the Davy Jones games… forever!

Enter a magic world of pirate adventure and find out if you can escape the curse of Davy Jones’ Locker next week!
